name: Vitalik Buterin - Decentral Eyes - Variant 06
description: 3D Z-space GIF variant artwork of the Ethereum founder. From 'Decentral Eyes' series. Created with 10+ images to create a decentralized portrait.Vitalik was the first portrait in the series. The series explores a variety of stereoscopic 3D methods for depth. Anything can happen with a variant tho, including this 3D style that happened first with the Andreas Antonopoulos animation. Newer works can influence older works. All in the flow... Only one of each variant artwork will be released.
